{"title":"人类衰退之后","uid":"661ada8f20043b5966559db7e08a1c48","slug":"art-3","date":"2023-10-28T02:04:12.000Z","updated":"2023-10-28T05:17:44.347Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/art-3.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/ac1.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"人类衰退之后漫评\"><a href=\"#人类衰退之后漫评\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"人类衰退之后漫评\"></a>人类衰退之后漫评</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"/>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"/>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"/>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"/>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"/>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"/>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"/>\n</svg>\n</span><p>原文记于2021-09-21</p></blockquote>\n<p>由田中罗密欧（写了“万能的人类圣经”rewrite）的轻小说漫改，12集乱序改编了6卷内容，以单元剧的形式完整地讲了几个故事。</p>\n<p>初看一眼画风柔和简洁，但剧情会让人懵逼，原因在于大量背景信息的缺失，或者按照评论区中的一个词来讲是”模糊”。 没有一个角色有确切的名字，每个角色都是由其特征所起的外号作为称呼。同时“怎么衰退”“为什么衰退”都没有讲，更甚连“人类”这一对象都是模糊的，这部番直接把脑洞大开的故事拍在你的脸上，用柔美画风包裹一些富有深度的思考（媒体曝光，时间悖论，人类发展等等）。</p>\n<p> 乱序叙事对观众的理解和记忆能力有一定要求，如果不习惯乱序可以选择按照b站评论区提供的顺序观看，那样的话时间线是没毛病的；但也会失去乱序的魅力，即碎片信息整合过程所提供的快感。 若是当做萌系日常番，没什么问题，总之我个人看完就有种“我虽然只能看懂一些，但我大受震撼”的感觉。（和七月番漂流男孩相比这个应该更好懂一些） </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://manuforest-blog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/ac2.png\" alt=\"ac2\"></p>\n<p><strong>总结:赶紧把它加入你的补番列表！（恳求）</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"后记\"><a href=\"#后记\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"后记\"></a>后记</h4></blockquote>\n<p><em>当年还不是声优厨的自己完全没有意识到女主CV中原麻衣的好，现在回想起来那配的属实是把粉中带黑演绎地淋漓尽致</em>🤤🤤</p>\n","text":"人类衰退之后漫评 原文记于2021-09-21 由田中罗密欧（写了“万能的人类圣经”rewrite）的轻小说漫改，12集乱序改编了6卷内容，以单元剧的形式完整地...","permalink":"/post/art-3","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":521,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"AniComments","slug":"AniComments","count":1,"path":"api/categories/AniComments.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"动漫简评","slug":"动漫简评","count":1,"path":"api/tags/动漫简评.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E8%A1%B0%E9%80%80%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%E6%BC%AB%E8%AF%84\"><span class=\"toc-text\">人类衰退之后漫评</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%90%8E%E8%AE%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">后记</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Manuforest","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/3.png","link":"/","description":"不知何时会脱宅的Galgame玩家 <br /> @ <b>记录没有失去的瞬间</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Manuforest","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/94931514?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"},"mail":{"icon